The convert folder is for making the linvstxconvert and linvstxconverttree (navigates subfolders) utilities that name convert Windows vst dll filenames (.dll) to corresponding Linux shared library filenames (.so).

Makefile makes linvstxconvert

Makefile-linxconverttree make linvstxconverttree

Makefiles need the gtk3 dev libraries

--------

The makegtk etc files in the convert folder contain simple commands for making the convert utilities.

A -no-pie option might be needed on some systems for the linvstxconvert and linvstxconverttree utilities icons to appear.
